beer.beer_description: Jungle Juice is an Imperial IPA made to emulate the feeling of getting punched in the face by Rambo. It's brewed with our favorite hop, Nelson Sauvin, along with considerable doses of Chinook, Galaxy, Mosaic, and Centennial, lending it a solid tropical-fruity nose. To give the hops the stage they deserve, Jungle Juice is brewed without any specialty malts, apart from wheat and oats which give it an uncharacteristically smooth mouthfeel.
